These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
There 2 different types of food: plum, zucchini
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up
1. the egyptian is on the far right##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Nationality       | turkish       | egyptian |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Food       | zucchini    | plum    |
| Beverage   | 7up       | milk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
City: san-francisco, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, photography
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| City      | edinburgh     | san-francisco |
| Birthday           | march | february      |
| Hobby   | photography  | board-games      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, japanese
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, animation
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the polish is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Nationality      | polish | japanese  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Hobby   | writing  | magic-tricks   |
| Movie-Genre     | animation     | romance |

