.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, cycling
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall
2 different pets are kept: hamster, snake
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | climbing       | cycling |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | aristoff    |
| Pet   | hamster           | snake   |

