1. the person who's hobby is chess is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
