.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, january
1. the coach is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Beverage   | mirinda          | almond-milk |
| Sport           | water-polo          | climbing    |
| Birthday     | january            | july       |

 